@startuml sequence-tc3-create-poi-auto-qr
title TC3 — Tạo POI → Tự động sinh QR thuyết minh
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

actor "Admin"     as A
participant "Admin Web" as Web
participant "POST /api/v1/pois" as PoiApi
participant "POST /api/v1/admin/qr/narration" as QrApi
participant "QRCoder"  as QR
database    "DB"       as DB

A   -> Web   : Điền form POI → Nhấn Lưu
Web -> PoiApi : { name, lat, lng, narrationText, ... }
PoiApi -> DB  : INSERT Pois → poiId=42
PoiApi -> DB  : INSERT PoiLanguage × 5 ngôn ngữ\n(auto-translate Azure Translator)
PoiApi --> Web : { poiId: 42 }

Web -> QrApi : { poiId:42, languageTag:"vi-VN" }
QrApi -> DB  : INSERT PoiTickets { ticketCode:"QR-A3F7", MaxUses:5 }
QrApi -> QR  : GenerateQrPng(JSON payload)
QR --> QrApi : byte[] png
QrApi --> Web : { ticketCode, qrImageBase64 }

Web -> A : Popup: ✅ POI #42 tạo xong\n[QR IMAGE]  Mã: QR-A3F7

== Du khách quét QR ==
actor "Du khách" as U
participant "Landing /p/QR-A3F7" as Page

U -> Page : Quét QR
Page -> DB : SELECT PoiTickets JOIN Pois + PoiLanguage
DB --> Page : { name, narrationText, lang }
Page -> U  : Render trang + phát TTS thuyết minh 🔊
@enduml
